---
// CustomerSegments.astro
---
<section class="section section-customers" id="customers">
  <div class="customer-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">🏦 Who It's For</div>
      <h2>Built for regulated organizations deploying agentic AI.</h2>
      <p>Causality is designed for institutions operating under regulatory scrutiny where AI systems must be explainable, auditable, and production-ready.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="segments-grid">
      <div class="segment-card card segment--primary" id="segment-banks" style="animation: slide-up 0.7s ease both 0.1s;">
        <div class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏦</div>
        <h3>Regional & Mid-Market Banks</h3>
        <p class="segment-why">Deploying agentic AI under DORA, SR 26-2, and evolving AI governance requirements - without the internal infrastructure needed to reconstruct AI incidents at scale.</p>
        <p class="segment-why">Causality provides the forensic visibility needed to safely operationalize AI systems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="segment-card card segment--secondary" id="segment-fintechs" style="animation: slide-up 0.7s ease both 0.25s;">
        <div class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">🚀</div>
        <h3>Regulated FinTechs</h3>
        <p class="segment-why">Scaling AI-driven financial products while maintaining auditability, incident traceability, and governance readiness across rapidly evolving systems.</p>
        <p class="segment-why">Causality helps modern AI infrastructure remain explainable under regulatory scrutiny.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.customer-glow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 60vw;
  height: 60vw;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: -1;
  animation: floatGlow 20s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.section-customers {
  overflow: hidden;
}

.segments-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.segment-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  position: relative;
}

.segment--primary {
  border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.25);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 100%);
}

.segment--primary:hover {
  border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.45);
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
}

.segment-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.segment-icon {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.25rem;
  right: 1.25rem;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  opacity: 0.55;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.25));
  transition: all var(--transition-base);
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}

.segment-card:hover .segment-icon {
  opacity: 0.8;
  transform: scale(1.08);
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4));
}

.segment-why { font-size: 0.9rem; }
.segment-why strong { color: var(--color-cyan); }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .segments-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .customer-glow { animation: none; }
  .segment-card { animation: none !important; }
  .segment-icon { transition: none; }
}
</style>
